#. RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.CREATURES.SPECIES.GEYSER.MOLTENSALTGEYSER.NAME
msgctxt "RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.CREATURES.SPECIES.GEYSER.MOLTENSALTGEYSER.NAME"
