#. RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.CREATURES.SPECIES.GEYSER.NITROGENVENT.DESC
msgctxt "RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.CREATURES.SPECIES.GEYSER.NITROGENVENT.DESC"
